Recall that Hanifa Abubakar was kidnapped on December 4th 2021on her way home.
Moreover, Her body was however recovered on Thursday in a shallow grave at a private school, Noble Kids Academy, at Kwanar Dakata, in the Nassarawa Local Government Area, Kano State.
Furthermore, Picture of Hanifa and her parents was recently shared by a popular Facebook page. Check out the screen capture of the post below;
However, A family member of a Hanifa Abubakar, has revealed that the prime suspect in the deceased’s death and abduction in Kano State was among the first set of people who sympathized with her parents after her disappearance.
According to reports, Hanifa Abubakar was the only child of her parents. Below is picture of Hanifa and her parents before she died;
In addition, Picture of Hanifa and her parents have generated many reactions by some users on the microblogging platform.
Conclusively, May her gentle soul continue to rest in peace.


